articles.title: Teenage girl killed in shark attack while swimming at Australia tourist spot - CNN
articles.description: A female swimmer has died in a shark attack in the waters off a popular tourist spot on Australia’s east coast, authorities said.
articles.content:
Sydney, AustraliaReuters
